text: Maculileiopus maculipennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1958.Biolib.cz - Maculileiopus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Acanthocinini Category:Beetles described in 1958 Category:Taxa named by Stephan von Breuning
title: Maculileiopus maculipennis
